297
00:18:17,584 --> 00:18:19,835
creio saber o que fazer.

298
00:18:20,154 --> 00:18:22,333
Sheldon, tenho más notícias.

299
00:18:22,334 --> 00:18:23,289
Mais?

300
00:18:24,163 --> 00:18:25,548
Receio que sim.

301
00:18:25,549 --> 00:18:28,069
Sabes a galinha com caju
que te trago nas Segundas à noite?

302
00:18:28,070 --> 00:18:30,251
Sim. Do Szechuan Palace.

303
00:18:31,051 --> 00:18:34,422
O Szechuan Palace
fechou há dois anos.

304
00:18:36,284 --> 00:18:38,010
